Packaging for PIDIP. PIDIP is written by Yves Degoyon.

You can find the original software at: http://ydegoyon.free.fr/pidip.html

Patches in debian/patches including build patch and some small fixes.

This packaging also makes the build compatible with pdp-caedes version of PDP (by Tom Schouten).

The package itself is based off the one from https://launchpad.net/~puredyne-team/+archive/ppa
Our repo is at: https://launchpad.net/~delvj/+archive/ubuntu/ppa

 - caedes
